name: rdflib-jsonld

pre_pr_migrator_status.pypy37: not solvable: master: ['linux_64_python3.7.____73_pypy: Encountered problems while solving.\nProblem: package rdflib-5.0.0-py36h9f0ad1d_0 requires python_abi 3.6.* *_cp36m, but none of the providers can be installed\n']

raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "rdflib-jsonld" %}
{% set version = "0.6.2" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 107cd3019d41354c31687e64af5e3fd3c3e3fa5052ce635f5ce595fd31853a63

build:
  number: 3
  script: '{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed -vvv '
  skip: true  # [py < 37 and aarch64]

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python
  run:
    - python
    - rdflib >=5.0.0

test:
  imports:
    - rdflib_jsonld

about:
  home: https://github.com/RDFLib/rdflib-jsonld
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_family: BSD
  license_file: LICENSE.md
  summary: rdflib extension adding JSON-LD parser and serializer
  dev_url: https://github.com/RDFLib/rdflib-jsonld

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - croth1
